    <p>The customer then analyzed the clean oil sample from our test. There was a significant reduction in the used engine oil's heavy metal and ash contamination.</p>
    <p>Dolphin Centrifuge recommended an oversized centrifuge. This was based on the flow-rate reduction required for ash removal. The following table summarizes the technical specifications of the centrifuge supplied by Dolphin.</p>
